name: Cmpsol Technology
overview:
Cmpsol technology is a trusted company of remote computer support. We provide online live technical support to resolve any type of PC related problems through phone, email and live chat. Since inception, we have been serving millions of computer users with a fleet of Microsoft Certified Systems Engineers. We are successful in providing computer repair and tech support solutions for all sorts of niggling computer problems.

We understand essential technical needs of the PC users and work accordingly. Cmpsol technology not only assists sole users but also have a demonstrated track record of offering remote computer help to small and medium-sized business houses as well. We employ experienced professionals to provide a harmonious support 24x7, round the year. At Cmpsol technology we cover wide range of services from basic computer set-up to critical software and hardware issues. In addition, we also offer Apple product support and MP3 player support to the users.

Our vision is to be the conclusive solution for all your technical needs by offering authentic computer support solutions at affordable price. With the best level of expertise, we take the responsibility of keeping your system error free and protected from vulnerabilities. Our goal is to eliminate all your technical hazards with prompt attention, quality service and uniform support.

Company Highlights, Specialties & Features: Virus Removal Computer Optimization Operating System Wireless Network Printers and Music Players
